
Blake N. Cooper

Blake N. Cooper is the Communications & Marketing Manager at UC Davis Study Abroad. A Saint Mary’s College of California graduate, Blake has been working in higher education for over ten years—at Saint Mary’s College, University of Washington, and UC Davis—in marketing, communications, social media, and alumni relations. Creator and managing editor of the awardwinning study abroad social media and creativity hub at UC Davis—The Aggies Abroad Network (www.UCDavisAbroad.com)—Blake can be found @BlakeNCooper.
